        "subject": "LU-18876 build: remove Lustre header autoMakefiles",
        "message": "LU-18876 build: remove Lustre header autoMakefiles\n\nThe Lustre header autoMakefiles just explicitly list\nout the name of each distributed header. We can detect\nthe headers automatically in the top-level autoMakefile.\nSo remove the explicit autoMakefiles in lustre/include/.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Timothy Day <timday@amazon.com>\nChange-Id: I5bdf83eb62bb7f19cf145cff4c0e89694264cb34\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/59414\nReviewed-by: Arshad Hussain <arshad.hussain@aeoncomputing.com>\nReviewed-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
